Recovery,gov,gives,transparency,to,the,funds,made,available,by,the,American,Recovery,and,Reinvestment,Act,of,The,website,allows,taxpayers,to,track,how,and,where,Recovery,funds,are,spent,as,well,as,reporting,of,potential,fraud,waste,and,abuse,The,API,gives,developers,access,to,Recovery,data,It,uses,the,REST,protocol,and,returns,responses,in,XML